@baseUrl = http://localhost:3333
@providerId = 1
@accessToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwicHJvdmlkZXJJZCI6MSwiZW1haWwiOiJqb2FvQGJhcmJlYXJpYS5jb20iLCJ0b2tlblR5cGUiOiJhY2Nlc3MiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzcyOTg5NzEsImV4cCI6MTc3NzI5OTg3MX0.oftZAiaohEfIqmMFcKLbnH7A9I3hlfjUoy9jix5vevg

### [SUCESSO] Criar horário válido na segunda-feira
# Esperado: 201 com objeto do horário criado
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "12:00"
}

###

### [SUCESSO] Criar segundo horário no mesmo dia sem sobreposição (adjacente)
# Esperado: 201 — horários adjacentes são permitidos
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "13:00",
  "endTime": "18:00"
}

###

### [SUCESSO] Criar horário em dia diferente
# Esperado: 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "friday",
  "startTime": "08:00",
  "endTime": "17:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] Criar horário com conflito de sobreposição
# Esperado: 409 ConflictError
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "10:00",
  "endTime": "14:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] Criar horário com prestador inexistente
# Esperado: 404 NotFoundError
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/999999/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "17:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] dayOfWeek com valor inválido (em português)
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error com campo dayOfWeek nos issues
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "segunda",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "17:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] startTime com formato inválido
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error com campo startTime nos issues
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "9h00",
  "endTime": "17:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] endTime com formato inválido
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error com campo endTime nos issues
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "99:99"
}

###

### [FALHA] startTime maior que endTime
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error com campo startTime nos issues
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "18:00",
  "endTime": "09:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] startTime igual a endTime
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}/schedules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "09:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] providerId inválido no path
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/abc/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "17:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] Sem token de autenticação
# Esperado: 401 UnauthorizedError
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}/schedules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "17:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] Token de outro prestador (sem permissão para criar horário para este providerId)
# Pré-requisito: @accessToken pertence ao prestador id=2; tentando criar horário para id=1
# Esperado: 403 ForbiddenError
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "17:00"
}
